#  System Architecture – Cloud Cost Monitoring & Prediction Dashboard

##  Overview

This project follows a **modular, multi-layered architecture** that separates responsibilities across different components:

* **Frontend Layer** → Visualization & user interaction
* **Java Application Layer** → Core processing & API integration
* **Machine Learning Layer (Flask)** → Cost prediction
* **Data Layer** → Dataset storage & preprocessing

This design ensures **scalability, maintainability, and real-world relevance**.

---

