##  Future Enhancement (Spring Boot Upgrade)

In the next phase, the Java application will be upgraded to **Spring Boot**.

**Planned Improvements:**
* Convert the Core Java app into a RESTful backend.
* Integrate the frontend into `resources/static`.
* Add a database layer (MySQL/Firebase).
* Implement real-time APIs.

**Updated Architecture:**
```text
Frontend → Spring Boot Backend → Flask ML API → Model
```

