##  FAQ

**Q: Why use Flask instead of Java for Machine Learning?**
> **A:** Python provides superior support and an extensive ecosystem for machine learning libraries like Scikit-learn, TensorFlow, and PyTorch. Flask is used as a lightweight wrapper to expose the ML model as a microservice API, while Java continues to handle the heavy lifting of the core application logic.

